## Phase 1 : Define app requirments (Before coding)
 - Dashboard screen
 - Real-time data update
 - Visual accident alert
 Data app will read from Cloud:
   > speed: ...
   > accident: true
   > status: "..."
   > lastUpdate: 00000000
   > location: ...

## Phase 2 : UI/UX Design (Before coding)
   - Splash screen 
   - Dashboard screen
      -- Status indicator:  Green / Red
      -- Speed gauge
      -- Accident alert banner
      -- Last update time
      -- location
        ( Draw design in figma )

